
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Calculator Page</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/CalculatorHomeCSS.css" />
    <noscript><link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/nosciptCSS.css" /></noscript>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b4662c256f.js" crossorgin="anonymous"></script> <!-- font icons -->
</head>
<body class="is-preload">

    <!-- Wrapper -->
    <div id="wrapper" class="divided">

        <!-- HeadingSection -->
        <section class="banner style1 orient-left content-align-left image-position-right fullscreen onload-image-fade-in onload-content-fade-right">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>Fitness Calculators</h1>
                <p class="major">Using a fitness calculator is the perfect way to make every part of your fitness journey more systematic and successful.The following is a complete list of our fitness and health related calculators.</p>
                <ul class="actions stacked">
                    <li><a href="#first" class="button big wide smooth-scroll-middle">Get Started</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.6fb081caa5419fedfc7ec1a081cf15a9?rik=RCM9hDoa3StMUg&pid=ImgRaw&r=0" alt="" />
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Cal1 -->
        <section class="spotlight style1 orient-right content-align-left image-position-center onscroll-image-fade-in" id="first">
            <div class="content">
                <h2>BMI  Calculator</h2>
                <p>The Body Mass Index (BMI) Calculator can be used to calculate BMI value and corresponding weight status while taking age into consideration.BMI is a measurement of a person's leanness or corpulence based on their height and weight, and is intended to quantify tissue mass. It is widely used as a general indicator of whether a person has a healthy body weight for their height.</p>
                <ul class="actions stacked">
                    <li><a href="/Users/Calcform" class="button">Learn More</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="https://is4-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple128/v4/91/a2/ba/91a2ba32-65a8-1116-c0ee-3d3ea01494a4/source/512x512bb.jpg" alt="" />
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Cal2 -->
        <section class="spotlight style1 orient-left content-align-left image-position-center onscroll-image-fade-in">
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Calorie Calculator</h2>
                <p>The Calorie Calculator can be used to estimate the number of calories a person needs to consume each day. This calculator can also provide some simple guidelines for gaining or losing weight.This Calorie Calculator is based on several equations, and the results of the calculator are based on an estimated average.</p>
                <ul class="actions stacked">
                    <li><a href="/Calorie/CalcCform" class="button">Learn More</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.adf4d33027fd80049e9a2054810ffc8e?rik=ZyQJZAbVkjMrAQ&pid=ImgRaw&r=0" alt="" />
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Cal3 -->
        <section class="spotlight style1 orient-right content-align-left image-position-center onscroll-image-fade-in">
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Ideal Weight Calculator</h2>
                <p>The Ideal Weight Calculator computes ideal body weight (IBW) ranges based on height, gender, and age. The idea of finding the IBW using a formula has been sought after by many experts for a long time. Currently, there persist several popular formulas, and our Ideal Weight Calculator provides their results for side-to-side comparisons.</p>
                <ul class="actions stacked">
                    <li><a href="#" class="button">Learn More</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="image">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.3f57f5c9e0d9914c98d9c7be6aa34730?rik=1ev7CWY93R1PWA&riu=http%3a%2f%2fpendidikanpesakit.myhealth.gov.my%2fwp-content%2fuploads%2f2016%2f05%2f06.png&ehk=UVpG90L5N5kIYTjvPb10Q5qyFRYtN5pKtHZaWPQ6cn4%3d&risl=&pid=ImgRaw&r=0" alt="" />
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Last section -->
        <section class="wrapper style1 align-center">
            <div class="inner medium">
                <h2>Having Issues ? Let us know</h2>
                <form method="post" action="#">
                    <div class="fields">
                        <div class="field half">
                            <label for="name">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" name="name" id="name" value="" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="field half">
                            <label for="email">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" name="email" id="email" value="" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="field">
                            <label for="message">Message</label>
                            <textarea name="message" id="message" rows="6"></textarea>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="actions special">
                        <li><input type="submit" name="submit" id="submit" value="Send Message" /></li>
                    </ul>
                </form>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="wrapper style1 align-center">
            <div class="inner">
                <ul class="icons">
                    <li><a href="#" class="icon brands style2 fa-twitter"><span class="label">Twitter</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="icon brands style2 fa-facebook-f"><span class="label">Facebook</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="icon brands style2 fa-instagram"><span class="label">Instagram</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="icon brands style2 fa-linkedin-in"><span class="label">LinkedIn</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="icon style2 fa-envelope"><span class="label">Email</span></a></li>
                </ul>
                <p>&copy; about us | sitemap | terms of use | privacy policy<a href="https://html5up.net"> © 2008 - 2023</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </footer>

    </div>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/jquery.scrollex.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/jquery.scrolly.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/browser.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/breakpoints.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/util.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/js/main.js"></script>

</body>
</html>